Make sure gst-rpicamsrc is installed from

https://github.com/thaytan/gst-rpicamsrc

Install the required packages:

sudo apt-get install python3 python3-gi python3-gst-1.0 pulseaudio \
	gstreamer1.0-plugins-{good,bad,ugly} gstreamer1.0-pulseaudio \
	gir1.2-gst-plugins-base-1.0 gir1.2-gstreamer-1.0 gir1.2-gst-rtsp-server-1.0
